- Must be at least 6 tiles away from a settlement.
- Must have at least 1x Monk bro
- Must have at least 1x Dervish bro
- Event has not happened in the past 30 days.

Outcome:
- Dervish bro receives +1-3 Health, receives a positive mood.
- Monk bro receives +1-3 Resolve, receives a positive mood.


